#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:5 94dd00828b0d485781203b844148ba3f
msgid "Can I use NotebookLM without an API key?"
msgstr "我可以在没有 API 密钥的情况下使用 NotebookLM 吗？"

#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:7 86d26dceca7742cdbe3ca02bc638c330
msgid ""
"**Yes.** Workspace management, file browsing, uploading, editing, and "
"GitHub cloning features work without any API key. Only AI chat and note "
"generation features require an API key. The UI will display a prompt "
"indicating that AI features are unavailable."
msgstr ""
"**可以。** 工作空间管理、文件浏览、上传、编辑和 GitHub 克隆功能无需 API 密钥即可使用。只有 AI 对话和笔记生成功能需要 "
"API 密钥。界面会显示提示，说明 AI 功能不可用。"

#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:9 4fcdeca514cb4ee1ad435a7891e2a0d1
msgid ""
"How do I use third-party compatible services (proxies, self-hosted "
"models)?"
msgstr "如何使用第三方兼容服务（代理、自托管模型）？"

#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:11 b3b2ed80e39a4488ab6bd3c4716c853c
msgid ""
"Set `OPENAI_BASE_URL` or `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL` in your `.env.local` file "
"to point to any API-compatible endpoint:"
msgstr ""
"在 `.env.local` 文件中将 `OPENAI_BASE_URL` 或 `ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL` 设置为任何 API "
"兼容的端点："

#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:18 49d24181a9274edb9fa4f47aa3188f1f
msgid ""
"If your proxy doesn't support the embedding endpoint, configure a "
"separate embedding service:"
msgstr "如果您的代理不支持 Embedding 端点，请配置单独的 Embedding 服务："

