#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:34 6e36c2226f274bfd82a96c298825407c
msgid "Is indexing slow for large workspaces?"
msgstr "大型工作空间的索引速度慢吗？"

#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:36 08f4c2589cf74ea99119b6962c96b5ac
msgid ""
"The first sync processes all files (extract text → chunk → generate "
"embeddings), which depends on the number and size of files. Subsequent "
"syncs only process new or modified files (based on file hash comparison),"
" making them significantly faster."
msgstr ""
"首次同步会处理所有文件（提取文本 → 分块 → "
"生成嵌入），速度取决于文件的数量和大小。后续同步仅处理新增或修改的文件（基于文件哈希比较），因此速度会显著加快。"

#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:38 88fb965914a746139c22d89cc93ead01
msgid "Can I run NotebookLM on Linux?"
msgstr "我可以在 Linux 上运行 NotebookLM 吗？"

#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:40 2b04e709e199455e9dce5fbd1bf9af35
msgid "**Yes.** Set `WORKSPACE_ROOTS` to Linux paths:"
msgstr "**可以。** 将 `WORKSPACE_ROOTS` 设置为 Linux 路径："

#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:46 427f5a44e1dc4f02bd9f09f94d3da129
msgid "GitHub clone fails — what should I check?"
msgstr "GitHub 克隆失败 —— 我应该检查什么？"

#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:48 92862828d1fb4bfbb4b05fb40eaae7e0
msgid "Verify that `git` is installed: `git --version`"
msgstr "验证 `git` 已安装：`git --version`"

#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:49 2c17b0385d9f4736a207d8e4e449de48
msgid "Check that `GITHUB_TOKEN` is set correctly in `.env.local`"
msgstr "检查 `.env.local` 中的 `GITHUB_TOKEN` 是否设置正确"

#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:50 0b29757a99e946d39bff88cc0d53c1e5
msgid "Ensure the token has the `repo` scope for private repositories"
msgstr "确保令牌具有用于私有仓库的 `repo` 权限范围"

#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:51 91372707fc9440f79ecd3f1244b81712
msgid "Check network connectivity to `github.com`"
msgstr "检查到 `github.com` 的网络连通性"

#: ../../troubleshooting/faq.md:53 328c31dfc1b643a58bd6e289f6bc884f
